"""
scrape_bmrb_solidstate.py — Fixed BMRB solid-state scraper.

Fixes vs v1 (per code review):
  1. PDB ID extraction now scans ALL saveframes and loops using PDB_RE pattern
     (not just 3 hardcoded tags)
  2. PDB_RE matches real PDB IDs: start with digit, 4 alphanum chars
     e.g. 1UBQ, 2M02, 7N4I — not UUID/BMRB/NMR etc.
  3. API fallback uses the same robust regex, not first-match of any 4-char string
  4. CIF parsing uses Bio.PDB.MMCIF2Dict for robustness on quoted fields
  5. Diagnostic mode: set DIAG_ID to inspect any failing entry's raw API response

Run LOCALLY (~15-30 min):
    conda activate nmr
    cd C:\\Users\\vamsi\\.vscode\\paravastu
    python src/scrape_bmrb_solidstate.py

Output: data/bmrb_ssNMR_candidates.csv
"""

